item.title: About me
item.description: My name is Yann Nicolas, I am a senior software architect currently living on the Space Coast in Florida, USA. I have been working in multiple countries (USA, Ireland, Mexico, France), businesses (Air Traffic Management, Banking, Urban Security, Avionics) and with seveal technology stacks (Java, .Net, Cloud stacks…). You can find more info on my LikedIn profile. Contact You can use Twitter or LikedIn to contact me.
